<br>
Hello Lashoon. <br>
So there you are. Did Karana think he could hide you from me merely by altering your soul. The old fool. He should know that my prey cannot be hidden from me for long. My only regret is that I was unable to warn you away from your present disastrous course. That I could have prevented your unfortunate union with Kishi. You see Lashoon, Kishi is very dear to me, I feel towards her as If she is ... Family. And I could not let you bring her to the depths of despair as you no doubt will. And now that there are your children... well all I can say is that so much needless death could have been avoided if I had been permitted to reach you earlier.<br>
Lashoon, it is your madness that will hurt your lovely Kishi more than your destruction. And I cannot allow such pain to enter my dear Kishi's life. In the fullness of time she will forget her fleeting time with you and your whelps. She has soo much time to look forward to. Ahh, Lashoon, I see I have you at a disadvantage. You see I have seen your pathetic life play out five times before. Always ending in burning madness destroying all you love. How dare you join your petty life to my dear Kishi's. But hold, I cannot deny that she is fond of you. And therefore I shall gift you Lashoon. I shall , for her sake, give you the thrill of the hunt. Shall I count to three? It always makes the hunt more interesting.<br>
<br>
For me. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm9.showPrevMessage?topicID=33.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm9.showNextMessage?topicID=33.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=33.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm9.emailToFriend?topicID=33.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm9.threadControl?topicID=33.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm9.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=33.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/fdraconisrampantfrm9.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=33.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub70.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="draconisrampantfrm2">The Dragon's Horde<option value="draconisrampantfrm4">Guild Events<option value="draconisrampantfrm7">The Dragon's Whisper<option value="draconisrampantfrm8">Msgs for Officers or Webmasters<option value="draconisrampantfrm9">Journals from the Battle